{"id":61448,"title":"Primary bone lymphoma of the left radius: a case report and related literature review.","abstract":"Primary bone lymphoma (PBL) is a rare but distinct clinicopathological disease. Because it is not common, the optimal treatment strategy has not been established. Here, we present a patient with PBL of the left radius and review the related literature. We focus on the standard treatment for PBL. Many aspects such as rehabilitation, local control and overall survival need to be considered. Studies on this disease should be carried out to clarify the optimal treatment in the future. ","date":"2014-04-14","categories":"Hemic and Lymphatic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24717101","annotations":[{"name":"Disease","weight":0.579145,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.553863,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Lymphoma","weight":0.432022,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lymphoma"},{"name":"Literature","weight":0.371872,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Literature"},{"name":"Physical therapy","weight":0.25977,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Physical_therapy"},{"name":"Bone","weight":0.231059,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bone"},{"name":"Case report","weight":0.157444,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Case_report"},{"name":"Patient","weight":0.101782,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Patient"},{"name":"Standardization","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standardization"},{"name":"Strategy","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Strategy"},{"name":"Radius","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Radius"},{"name":"Standard treatment","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Standard_treatment"},{"name":"Literature review","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Literature_review"},{"name":"Survival rate","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Survival_rate"},{"name":"Primary education","weight":0.0168322,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Primary_education"},{"name":"Mathematical optimization","weight":0.0136738,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mathematical_optimization"},{"name":"Problem-based learning","weight":0.013127,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Problem-based_learning"}]}
